{"tid":1161958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"史上容量最大的microSD卡開始出貨了，1TB要價450美元","createTime":"2019-05-19T14:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T23:08:49.000Z","uid":32511,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1e60a9ebd940327810eec6e9b66153bc7d03a2","tid":1161958,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"快閃記憶體業者SanDisk曾在今年2月提及的1TB超大容量microSD儲存記憶卡終於開始出貨了，近日正式於官網上架，預計也會舖貨到Amazon，售價為449.99美元（約為新台幣1.4萬元）。<br />\n <br />\n此款1TB記憶卡的全名為SanDisk Extreme microSD UHS-I Card，可適用於Android手機、數位相機、或是空拍機，由於容量巨大，因此可用來儲存大量的高畫質照片或影片，不必再擔心儲存空間不足的問題。<br />\n <br />\nSanDisk表示，該記憶卡可適應極端氣候、能夠防水、防衝擊，也禁得起機場的X光掃描，最快讀取速度為每秒90MB。它的防水等級為IPX7，代表可在1米深的清水或海水中支撐72小時，也能適應從攝氏零下25度到85度的天氣，可承受500Gs的衝擊，或是從5米高掉下來也沒事。<br />\n <br />\n這應該是目前全球容量最大的microSD記憶卡，但它的尺寸只有15mmx11mmx1mm，就有媒體打趣說，他無法想像要是遺失了存有1TB資料的microSD卡會是什麼樣的心情。"},{"pid":"9214d6bcaa690d66e09b877addf73954f67ec0c6","tid":1161958,"uid":56015,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:07:15.000Z","msg":"大有撚用咩, 整個300MBps read write 先啦"},{"pid":"6584808bff7c610b15cb4c1c4ade0d2b6f3277e4","tid":1161958,"uid":56015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9214d6bcaa690d66e09b877addf73954f67ec0c6","tid":1161958,"uid":56015,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:07:15.000Z","msg":"大有撚用咩, 整個300MBps read write 先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sdcard.org/developers/overview/bus_speed/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sdcard.org%2Fdevelopers%2Foverview%2Fbus_speed%2Findex.html&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPajPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=decb4653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sdcard.org/developers/overview/bus_speed/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"ca10e6e81c4808f2cd90f790ad1b99b4d40d3cc3","tid":1161958,"uid":40588,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/